4 types of squats to incorporate into your leg day for overall toning! 

This is what my leg day program was:
( 2 sets of):
- 25 squats with ball raise. ( works your arms & abs too)
- 25 kettle bell swings
- 25 jump squats 
- 25 military squats 

- 15 back lunges with barbell 
- 15 leg curls 
- 15 inner thigh pushes 
- 15 leg press 

Let me know if you have any questions! 💘💘

latestIgtvVideos.title: PUSH YOURSELF🍑
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Stupid Instagram blocked the vid with music so here’s the plain one with just the beeps.
•
•
•
A bear crawl works almost every muscle of your body!! This workout is just a super intense 5min workout:
• 40s crawl-20s hold x5. 
The 3rd set has a 20s break instead of a hold. So PUSH YOURSELF and challenge yourself to be able to do the complete 5min at a go by the end of the week. If you regularly workout and can do the entire 5min at a go, then your aim to do keep repeating it for as long as you can at a stretch!!

latestIgtvVideos.title: How to jump correctly
latestIgtvVideos.caption: So a lot of people have texted me about knee pain and back pain after exercising. Jumping incorrectly is a major cause of post workout injury. I hope this helps, feel free to send me a video if you want me to check it for you!!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Get your 🍑 moving
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A few stretches in bed right after you wake up gets your blood flowing and really helps you wake up and get fresh. It also really helps with muscle soreness!! If you’re lucky enough after you stretch in bed your body might also feel like going for a run :)) •
